Key Notes on Flow:

Covert vs Active weighting

Covert = subtle intent, hidden will, â€œwhat they truly wantâ€ â†’ lower numeric weight

Active = motivation, goal-oriented, energy to act â†’ higher weight

Multipliers at each step

Mood/emotion can amplify or dampen action probability.

